    the intro slide's shape (mascot, title, description, CTA) so the
    overlay animates in over a layout close to the final content. %>
<div class="shuby-questionnaire-overlay-skeleton" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="shuby-questionnaire-overlay-skeleton-mascot"></div>
  <div class="shuby-questionnaire-overlay-skeleton-title"></div>
  <div class="shuby-questionnaire-overlay-skeleton-line"></div>
  <div class="shuby-questionnaire-overlay-skeleton-line"></div>
  <div class="shuby-questionnaire-overlay-skeleton-line shuby-questionnaire-overlay-skeleton-line--short"></div>
  <div class="shuby-questionnaire-overlay-skeleton-button"></div>
</div>
